<p><img alt="Oil wells in Huntington Beach, 1935. Courtesy of the Frasher Foto Postcard Collection, Pomona Public Library." src="http://www.kcet.org/updaily/socal_focus/HB-oil-pomonapl.jpg" width="597" height="373" class="mt-image-none" style="" /></p>

